### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### PRISM AI Analytics — API Test Suite
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Install the "REST Client" extension in VS Code,
### then click "Send Request" above any request below.
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ─── Health Check (no auth required) ───
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### ─── Dashboard KPIs ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/dashboard

###

### ─── All Clients ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/clients

###

### ─── All Projects ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/projects

###

### ─── Pipeline (Leads) ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pipeline

###

### ─── Invoices ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/invoices

###

### ─── Expenses ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/expenses

###

### ─── Time Entries ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/time

###

### ─── Activity Log ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activity

###

### ─── Services ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/services

###

### ─── Certifications ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/certifications

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### CRM ENDPOINTS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ─── All CRM Customers ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/crm

###

### ─── Urgent Triggers ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/crm/triggers

###

### ─── Create a New Customer ───
POST http://localhost:3000/api/crm/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company": "Test Company LLC",
  "contactName": "Jane Doe",
  "contactEmail": "jane@testcompany.com",
  "contactPhone": "704-555-1234",
  "status": "New Lead",
  "service": "AI Readiness Assessment",
  "projectName": "Test — AI Assessment",
  "budget": 2500,
  "leadSource": "LinkedIn",
  "industry": "Technology",
  "notes": "Test record — safe to delete"
}

###

### ─── Update Customer Status ───
### (Replace :id with a real customer id from GET /api/crm)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/crm/customers/:id/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Discovery Scheduled",
  "notes": "Booked intro call for next Tuesday"
}

###

### ─── Update Customer Fields ───
### (Replace :id with a real customer id from GET /api/crm)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/crm/customers/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "crm_budget": 3500,
  "crm_service": "Analytics & Reporting Modernization"
}

###

### ─── Log Activity for a Customer ───
### (Replace :id with a real customer id from GET /api/crm)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/crm/activity/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "call",
  "summary": "Follow-up call — discussed project timeline"
}

###

### ─── Get Activity Log for a Customer ───
### (Replace :id with a real customer id from GET /api/crm)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/crm/activity/:id

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### VALIDATION TESTS (should return errors)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ─── Missing company (expect 400) ───
POST http://localhost:3000/api/crm/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactName": "No Company Person"
}

###

### ─── Invalid email (expect 400) ───
POST http://localhost:3000/api/crm/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company": "Bad Email Co",
  "contactEmail": "not-an-email"
}

###

### ─── Invalid status (expect 400) ───
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/crm/customers/:id/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Fake Status That Doesnt Exist"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AUTH TESTS (only relevant if API_KEY is set)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ─── With Bearer Token ───
### (Set your API_KEY value below)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/crm
Authorization: Bearer your-api-key-here

###

### ─── Bad Token (expect 403) ───
GET http://localhost:3000/api/crm
Authorization: Bearer wrong-key
